  'Site Work', 'Demo', 'Foundation', 'Framing', 'Roofing',
  'MEP', 'Plumbing', 'Electrical', 'HVAC', 'Insulation',
  'Drywall', 'Interior', 'Finishes', 'Landscaping', 'Inspections', 'General',
